#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:2583
msgid "MC is a very smart viewer.  This is a great tool for searching words in documents.  I always use this for files in the \"<literal>/usr/share/doc</literal>\" directory.  This is the fastest way to browse through masses of Linux information.  This viewer can be directly started using one of the following commands."
