msgid "The network interface served by the DHCP"
msgstr "Interfaces rseau gres par DHCP"

#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:12248
msgid "After prepairing the system by <xref linkend=\"_the_dhcp_connection_with_the_ethernet\"/>, the network interface served by the DHCP is configured by creating the configuration entry in the \"<literal>/etc/network/interfaces</literal>\" file as the following."
msgstr "Aprs avoir prpar le systme selon <xref linkend=\"_the_dhcp_connection_with_the_ethernet\"/>, l'interface rseau gre par le DHCP est configure en crant l'entre de configuration suivante dans le fichier &nbsp;<literal>/etc/network/interfaces</literal>&nbsp;&nbsp;:"

