msgid "Make configuration in \"<literal>/etc/network/interfaces</literal>\" only as the following."
msgstr "Ne mettez que ce qui suit dans le fichier de configuration &nbsp;<literal>/etc/network/interfaces</literal>&nbsp;&nbsp;:"

