msgid "For the DHCP (see <xref linkend=\"_the_network_interface_served_by_the_dhcp\"/>), you can replace pertinent <emphasis role=\"strong\"><literal>iface</literal></emphasis> stanza lines in the \"<literal>/etc/network/interfaces</literal>\" with the following."
msgstr "Pour le DHCP (voir <xref linkend=\"_the_network_interface_served_by_the_dhcp\"/>), vous pouvez remplacer les lignes d'entre <emphasis role=\"strong\"><literal>iface</literal></emphasis> pertinentes du fichier &nbsp;<literal>/etc/network/interfaces</literal>&nbsp; avec ce qui suit&nbsp;:"

