msgstr "&nbsp;<literal>RSAAuthentication</literal>&nbsp;&nbsp;: cl RSA pour SSH-1 (obsolte parce qu'il a t remplac)."

# type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><screen>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:15549
#, no-wrap
