msgid "Each package which is compliant to Freedesktop.org's xdg menu system installs its menu data provided by \"<literal>*.desktop</literal>\" under \"<literal>/usr/share/applications/</literal>\". Modern desktop environments which are compliant to Freedesktop.org standard use these data to generate their menu using the <literal>xdg-utils</literal> package.  See \"<literal>/usr/share/doc/xdg-utils/README</literal>\"."
