#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:22567
msgid "You should pay extra care to the backup and restoration of identity related data files such as \"<literal>/etc/ssh/ssh_host_dsa_key</literal>\", \"<literal>/etc/ssh/ssh_host_rsa_key</literal>\", \"<literal>~/.gnupg/*</literal>\", \"<literal>~/.ssh/*</literal>\", \"<literal>/etc/passwd</literal>\", \"<literal>/etc/shadow</literal>\", \"<literal>/etc/fetchmailrc</literal>\", \"<literal>popularity-contest.conf</literal>\", \"<literal>/etc/ppp/pap-secrets</literal>\", and \"<literal>/etc/exim4/passwd.client</literal>\".  Some of these data can not be regenerated by entering the same input string to the system."
msgstr "Vous devez prendre des prcautions supplmentaires lors de la sauvegarde et de la restauration des fichiers de donnes relatifs  l'identit comme &nbsp;<literal>/etc/ssh/ssh_host_dsa_key</literal>&nbsp;, &nbsp;<literal>/etc/ssh/ssh_host_rsa_key</literal>&nbsp;, &nbsp;<literal>~/.gnupg/*</literal>&nbsp;, &nbsp;<literal>~/.ssh/*</literal>&nbsp;, &nbsp;<literal>/etc/passwd</literal>&nbsp;, &nbsp;<literal>/etc/shadow</literal>&nbsp;, &nbsp;<literal>/etc/fetchmailrc</literal>&nbsp;, &nbsp;<literal>popularity-contest.conf</literal>&nbsp;, &nbsp;<literal>/etc/ppp/pap-secrets</literal>&nbsp; et &nbsp;<literal>/etc/exim4/passwd.client</literal>&nbsp;. Certaines de ces donnes ne peuvent pas tre recres  en entrant la mme chane de caractres d'entre sur le systme."

